  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic, ginger, cumin, coriander, and paprika. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chicken broth, honey, and lemon juice. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then cover the pot and transfer it to the oven.",
    "Bake for 2 1/2 hours, or until the lamb is tender.",
    "Stir in the chopped cilantro and season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
